      public Character(String name, String world, String desc, Integer win, Integer loss, String picture, String owner)
      Character Custom Constructor This is the character class custom constructor that creates a character object based on a set of parameters.
      Parameters:
      name - string name of character
      world - fanstasy world of character
      desc - description of character and abilites
      win - total number of wins
      loss - total number of losses
      picture - url for image of character
      owner - user who uploaded character
